<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ض غ ن:</span> <span class="c2">(الضِّغْنُ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(الضَّغِينَةُ)</span> الْحِقْدُ وَقَدْ <span class="c2">(ضَغِنَ)</span> عَلَيْهِ مِنْ بَابِ طَرِبَ. وَ <span class="c2">(تَضَاغَنَ)</span> الْقَوْمُ وَ <span class="c2">(اضْطَغَنُوا)</span> انْطَوَوْا عَلَى الْأَحْقَادِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>